        "answer": "Usually within 48–72 hours."
      },
      {
        "question": "What if the biopsy is inconclusive?",
        "answer": "A repeat or alternative imaging-guided biopsy may be advised."
      },
      {
        "question": "Any dietary restrictions post-procedure?",
        "answer": "Resume normal diet unless advised otherwise."
      }
